item.title: CVE-2023-2654|2024-08-02T06:26:09.906Z -- unknown -- conditional%20menus
item.description: The Conditional Menus WordPress plugin before 1.2.1 does not escape a parameter before outputting it back in an attribute, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
